{"nodes":[{"content":"Recording On/Off Transitions","pos":[11,39]},{"content":"Recording On/Off Transitions","pos":[53,81]},{"content":"Recording On/Off Transitions","pos":[270,298]},{"content":"Windows Performance Recorder (WPR) includes built-in profiles for on/off transitions.","pos":[301,386]},{"content":"You can record the following types of boot transition:","pos":[387,441]},{"pos":[447,513],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>On/Off - Boot<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>: Records performance while booting the computer."},{"pos":[519,619],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>On/Off - FastStartup<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>: Records performance during a Windows 8 Windows 8’s fast startup operation."},{"pos":[625,701],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>On/Off - Shutdown<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>: Records performance while shutting the computer down."},{"pos":[707,793],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>On/Off - RebootCycle<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>: Records performance during the entire cycle while rebooting."},{"pos":[799,905],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>On/Off - Standby/Resume<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>: Records performance when the computer is placed on standby, and then resumed."},{"pos":[911,1023],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>On/Off - Hibernate/Resume<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>: Records performance when the computer is placed in hibernation, and then resumed."},{"content":"By default, these profiles reboot the computer three times.","pos":[1025,1084]},{"pos":[1086,1135],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">*</bpt>On/off<ept id=\"p1\">*</ept> transitions are always logged to a file."},{"content":"Related topics","pos":[1140,1154]},{"content":"WPR Common Scenarios","pos":[1158,1178]},{"content":"Windows On/Off Transition Performance Analysis","pos":[1232,1278]},{"content":"Windows On/Off Transitions Solutions Guide","pos":[1331,1373]},{"content":"Results for the On/Off Assessments","pos":[1426,1460]},{"content":"On/Off Transition Performance","pos":[1517,1546]}],"content":"---\ntitle: Recording On/Off Transitions\ndescription: Recording On/Off Transitions\nMSHAttr:\n- 'PreferredSiteName:MSDN'\n- 'PreferredLib:/library/windows/hardware'\nms.assetid: 4fdf35b1-cbe9-4711-a0ac-a2241581425f\nms.prod: W10\nms.mktglfcycl: operate\nms.sitesec: msdn\n---\n\n# Recording On/Off Transitions\n\n\nWindows Performance Recorder (WPR) includes built-in profiles for on/off transitions. You can record the following types of boot transition:\n\n-   **On/Off - Boot**: Records performance while booting the computer.\n\n-   **On/Off - FastStartup**: Records performance during a Windows 8 Windows 8’s fast startup operation.\n\n-   **On/Off - Shutdown**: Records performance while shutting the computer down.\n\n-   **On/Off - RebootCycle**: Records performance during the entire cycle while rebooting.\n\n-   **On/Off - Standby/Resume**: Records performance when the computer is placed on standby, and then resumed.\n\n-   **On/Off - Hibernate/Resume**: Records performance when the computer is placed in hibernation, and then resumed.\n\nBy default, these profiles reboot the computer three times.\n\n*On/off* transitions are always logged to a file.\n\n## Related topics\n\n\n[WPR Common Scenarios](windows-performance-recorder-common-scenarios.md)\n\n[Windows On/Off Transition Performance Analysis](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?linkid=247578)\n\n[Windows On/Off Transitions Solutions Guide](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?linkid=247577)\n\n[Results for the On/Off Assessments](../assessments/results-for-the-onoff-assessments.md)\n\n[On/Off Transition Performance](../assessments/onoff-transition-performance.md)\n\n \n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n"}